sections.text: Terms, defined.For purposes of sections 67-446 to 67-453:(1) General partner means a partner in a partnership and a general partner in a limited partnership;(2) Limited partner means a limited partner in a limited partnership;(3) Limited partnership means a limited partnership created under the Nebraska Uniform Limited Partnership Act, predecessor law, or comparable law of another jurisdiction; and(4) Partner includes both a general partner and a limited partner.SourceLaws 1997, LB 523, ยง 46.Cross ReferencesNebraska Uniform Limited Partnership Act, see section 67-296.
